headlines.description: Crystal Palace came back from a goal down to win 5-1 at Leeds United to increase the Yorkshire club's fears of relegation on Sunday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Palace rout Leeds 5-1 as Hodgson revival goes on

headlines.description: A late goal by Roberto Firmino helped Liverpool come from two goals behind to secure a 2-2 draw with Premier League leaders Arsenal.
headlines.shortLinkText: Liverpool stun Arsenal to earn dramatic 2-2 draw
